Title: An Act Changing the Name of Basilan City Emergency Hospital in the Municipality of Lamitan, Province of Basilan, to Lamitan District Hospital
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 713
An Act Changing the Name of Basilan City Emergency Hospital in the Municipality of Lamitan, Province of Basilan, to Lamitan District Hospital
Section 1. The name of Basilan City Emergency Hospital in the Municipality of Lamitan, Province of Basilan, is hereby changed of Lamitan District Hospital.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
